body.p:
In your customization css add the following CSS
                rules:*[class ~= "map/map"]{
    string-set: number-of-words oxy_xpath("string-length(normalize-space(.)) - string-length(translate(normalize-space(.),' ','')) +1");
}

@page front-page {
     @bottom-center {
          content: "Number of words: " string(number-of-words);
     }
}This
                example counts all the words, including the ones from the TOC, but does not take into account the static
                labels.Preferably define the string set directly on the root element if you intend to use
                it in the front page.The context node for the XPath execution is(are) the one(s) matched by
                the CSS selector.
